                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7324" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1824</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8777 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">转型失败，*ST文化路在何方</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">When the transformation fails, where will *ST culture go in the future?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李振华，魏豆豆，张天</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东文化长城集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略转型；并购；公司治理；文化长城</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Strategic transformation; Merger and Acquisition; Corporate governance; Cultural Great Wall</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化长城是国内首家在创业板上市的创意艺术陶瓷企业，但上市后，业绩却并未按照预期快速增长，为了寻找新的利润点，公司开始实施战略转型，大举进军教育领域，收购了包括联汛教育、智游臻龙、翡翠教育在内的多家子公司。并购没有给文化长城带来转机，反而给公司埋下了经营隐患，最终引发了更大的问题。2021年10月，文化长城股票被实施其他风险警示。2022年5月，公司的经营情况进一步恶化，净资产已经为负值，被实施退市风险警示，股票简称变更为“*ST文化”。本案例追溯了文化长城从初创到战略转型再到转型失败的整个过程。案例旨在以文化长城为例，引导学员关注战略转型的含义与动机、并购的方式与风险以及公司治理的相关问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Cultural Great Wall is the first creative art ceramic enterprise listed on the gem in China, but after listing, its performance did not grow rapidly as expected. In order to find new profit points, the company began to implement strategic transformation, entered the field of education on a large scale, and acquired a number of subsidiaries including Lianxun education, Zhiyou Zhenlong and Feicui education. Merger and Acquisition did not bring a turnaround to Cultural Great Wall, but buried hidden dangers for the company, and finally caused greater problems. In October 2020, Cultural Great Wall stock was warned of other risks. In May 2022, the company&#39;s business situation further deteriorated, and its net assets had been negative. The delisting risk warning was implemented, and the stock abbreviation was changed to &quot;* ST culture&quot;. This case traces the whole process of Cultural Great Wall from start-up to strategic transformation and then to transformation failure. Taking Cultural Great Wall as an example, the case aims to guide students to pay attention to the meaning and motivation of strategic transformation, the ways and risks of M &amp; A, and the related issues of corporate governance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购》、《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略转型的内涵与动因；并购的种类与风险；信息不对称理论；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
